race.comment: BLACK MINTO (7) has hit a purple patch of late with a win and three placings from her past four starts. Hard to knock mares in form and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. DETRIMENTAL (3) is on the doorstep of another victory with consecutive runner-up finishes and this is not an overly strong affair. Can go one better against this line-up. WONFORWAZZA (5) has a handy record here on his home circuit with a win and three seconds from seven spins. Can run a race while fresh. SCOUNDREL (4) grows a leg for hoop Lloyd who has two wins from as many steers. Include from the inside alley. THE CATCH (1) next in line with the 3kg claim.
